com.bigdata.btree.raba.codec

Class RandomURIGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bigdata.btree.raba.codec.RandomURIGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRabaGenerator

    public class RandomURIGenerator
extends Object
implements IRabaGenerator
    Generate n random and distinct URIs. This distribution has a shared prefix followed by some random bytes representing an integer value. There are no nulls, even for the B+Tree values.
